race.comment: TRICKETEER (1) was out of the money two runs back then just missed the frame last start over 1300m at Ewan, beaten 6 lengths into fourth. Looks well placed so expect a big run this time. MISTER MODERATION (5) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1350m at Julia Creek, beaten 7 lengths into sixth. Taking on a better line-up this time but he is up to the challenge. LAST DITCH EFFORT (2) missed the frame last time when sixth at Cloncurry. Prior to that had been in the money on three consecutive occasions. Should camp just off the leaders and has winning claims on best figures. PEACEFUL PRINCE (4) was well found in the betting last time out but could only manage to finish fifth over 1400m at Charleville. On his best form he is capable of testing his rivals.
